data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT    A lovely home located in the Silver Lake Forest subdivision, has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a living room, a family room and a huge screened-in lanai.  This home has plenty of yard space in the front and the back and could be great for entertaining.  The home is less than a mile from Via Port Mall and many restaurants. This nice, quiet community is waiting to welcome you home.  For a private tour please give me a call.
